desc: Cover and disguise your Ring Camera, Wyze Camera, Blink Mini & Nest Cam with Camasker. Conceal your home security camera and turn it into a hidden camera with Camasker. Camasker is an artificial plant housing case designed for Ring Indoor Cam, Ring Stick Up Cam, Wyze Cam V3, Wyze Cam V2, Blink Mini & Nest Cam Indoor.
